// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2897 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b28ae282-d53d-5d1f-a011-9283e5501076

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
